original_title: Ja, Dat Was Høken, 40 Jaar Normaal
overview: This is the story of the dutch rock and roll/blues band 'Normaal'. Started by artist/farmers hero/lyrrical genius Bennie Jolink. It shows the start and end of the 50 year journey that was Normaal,and the impact on dutch society.
title: Ja, Dat Was Høken, 40 Jaar Normaal
